- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper establishes the complexity of the satisfiability and finite satisfiability problems. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is possible as the paper deals with the complexity of decision problems. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with logical reasoning and quantifiers, which are relevant to AI.
